commit.message:
Update character encoding list

Added a few more known encodings. Now includes the SAS names as
documented here:

http://support.sas.com/documentation/cdl/en/nlsref/61893/HTML/default/viewer.htm#a002607278.htm
length of header can be different from 1024 and 8192
character encoding header field; contributed by Evan Miller; unverified
add 'encoding' argument for string data; contributed by Philipp Pagel <Philipp.Pagel@numares.com>
align data reading frame to 'double' bondary; this had been removed previously; preparations for v0.5
add debug argument that returns entire function environment as attribute
README only refers to vignette, rather than .rst file
moved vignette data to preferred location
draft implementation of u64 support completed
